title: Exit Interview: The Ousted Contestant Is Pissed That She Was Eliminated for Dancing and Not Runway or a Photoshoot
text:
Exit Interview: The Ousted Contestant Is Pissed That She Was Eliminated for Dancing and Not Runway or a Photoshoot Another one bites the dust :( by Damian Bellino 2h ago 
It’s been a doozy of a week with two of the America’s Next Top Model contestants going home in the same week. Panelist Law Roach sat down with the most recently eliminated model to get all the details of her exit, the future of her modeling career, and obviously her complicated relationships with Kyle and Courtney .
